title: Yummy apple spice muffins
ingredients: ['110g butter, room temperature', '135g caster sugar', '2 eggs', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 tablespoon ground allspice', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '235ml apple sauce', '190g plain flour', '1 teaspoon dark brown soft sugar', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
